title: Roburritos
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, American, Fast food, Take-out, Mexican, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. A lowbrow (on purpose) burrito and quesadilla joint with several locations. Offers the choice of potato filling instead of meat. Vegans to specify--ask to omit cheese, sour cream, etc. Note: the Texas Hold'em BBQ sauce in the BBQ burrito contains honey. American style burritos, comes in 2 sizes.
